commentText:
Creates a source reading {@link WikipediaEditEvent} instances from the_specified IRC channel.__

In most cases, you want to use the default {@link #WikipediaEditsSource}_constructor. This constructor is meant to be used only if there is a_problem with the default constructor.__@param host The IRC server to connect to._@param port The port of the IRC server to connect to._@param channel The channel to join. Messages not matching the expected_format will be ignored.
codeText: public WikipediaEditsSource(String host, int port, String channel) {_		this.host = host__		this.port = port__		this.channel = channel__	}
